{"id": "art-25177", "label": "Art. 25177", "title": "Art. 25177", "slug": "art-25177", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_474229003\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1203\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_474229003\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>77</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_351242579\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1202\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_351242579\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>O divizare\ntransfrontalier&#259; complet&#259; are, de la data prev&#259;zut&#259; la art.\n251<sup>76</sup>, urm&#259;toarele efecte:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1522345487\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1201\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1522345487\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)toate activele <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pasivele\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care face obiectul\ndiviz&#259;rii sunt transferate c&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nbeneficiare potrivit repartiz&#259;rii prev&#259;zute în proiectul de divizare\ntransfrontalier&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1867186271\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1200\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1867186271\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)<span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care face obiectul diviz&#259;rii\ndevin <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span> ai <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nbeneficiare în <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> de alocare a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau altor titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social\nprev&#259;zute în proiectul de divizare transfrontalier&#259;, cu <span\nclass=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> cazului în care <span class=SpellE>ace&#351;tia</span>\nau exercitat dreptul de retragere, potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nart. 251<sup>69</sup>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1540273770\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1199\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1540273770\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)drepturile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ncare face obiectul diviz&#259;rii ce decurg din contractele de munc&#259; sau\ndin raporturile de munc&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> care\nexist&#259; la data de la care divizarea transfrontalier&#259; produce efecte\nse transfer&#259; <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> beneficiare,\npotrivit repartiz&#259;rii prev&#259;zute în proiectul de divizare\ntransfrontalier&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1952816209\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1198\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1952816209\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)societatea care face obiectul diviz&#259;rii <span\nclass=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> înceteaz&#259; <span class=SpellE>existen&#355;a</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_960055262\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1197\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_960055262\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>O divizare\ntransfrontalier&#259; <span class=SpellE>par&#355;ial&#259;</span> are, de la\ndata prev&#259;zut&#259; la art. 251<sup>76</sup>, urm&#259;toarele efecte:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1898362542\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1196\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1898362542\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)o parte din activele <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\npasivele <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care face obiectul\ndiviz&#259;rii sunt transferate c&#259;tre societatea sau <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nbeneficiare, potrivit repartiz&#259;rii prev&#259;zute în proiectul de divizare\ntransfrontalier&#259;, restul activelor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\npasivelor continuând s&#259; fac&#259; parte din patrimoniul <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> divizate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2024360078\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1195\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2024360078\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> unii dintre <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ncare face obiectul diviz&#259;rii devin <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span>\nai <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> beneficiare <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> o parte\ndintre <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span> r&#259;mân în societatea care\nface obiectul diviz&#259;rii sau devin <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span> ai ambelor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>,\nîn <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> de alocare a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de\nvaloare reprezentând capitalul social prev&#259;zute în proiectul de divizare\ntransfrontalier&#259;, cu <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> cazului în\ncare <span class=SpellE>ace&#351;tia</span> au exercitat dreptul de retragere,\npotrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>69</sup>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1565160061\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1194\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1565160061\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)drepturile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ncare face obiectul diviz&#259;rii ce decurg din contractele de munc&#259; sau\ndin raporturile de munc&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> care\nexist&#259; la data de la care divizarea transfrontalier&#259; produce efecte\nse transfer&#259; <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> beneficiare\nsau r&#259;mân în patrimoniul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ndivizate, potrivit repartiz&#259;rii prev&#259;zute în proiectul de divizare\ntransfrontalier&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_323132097\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1193\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_323132097\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>O divizare\ntransfrontalier&#259; prin separare are, de la data prev&#259;zut&#259; la art.\n251<sup>76</sup>, urm&#259;toarele efecte:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_77812720\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1192\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_77812720\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)o parte din activele <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\npasivele <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care face obiectul\ndiviz&#259;rii este transferat&#259; c&#259;tre societatea sau <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> beneficiare, potrivit\nrepartiz&#259;rii prev&#259;zute în proiectul de divizare\ntransfrontalier&#259;, restul activelor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\npasivelor continuând s&#259; fac&#259; parte din patrimoniul <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> divizate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2108722423\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1191\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2108722423\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ile</span> sociale sau alte titluri de valoare\nreprezentând capitalul social la societatea beneficiar&#259;/<span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> beneficiare se aloc&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care face obiectul diviz&#259;rii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1406520942\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1190\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1406520942\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)drepturile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ncare face obiectul diviz&#259;rii ce decurg din contractele de munc&#259; sau\ndin raporturile de munc&#259;, care exist&#259; la data de la care divizarea\ntransfrontalier&#259; produce efecte, se transfer&#259; <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> beneficiare, potrivit\nrepartiz&#259;rii prev&#259;zute în proiectul de divizare\ntransfrontalier&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_300276799\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1189\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_300276799\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)În cazul în care un element de activ sau un element de\npasiv al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care face obiectul\ndiviz&#259;rii nu este repartizat în proiectul de divizare\ntransfrontalier&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> dac&#259; interpretarea\ntermenilor proiectului nu permite luarea unei decizii privind repartizarea sa,\nelementul de activ ori contravaloarea sau, dup&#259; caz, elementul de pasiv se\nrepartizeaz&#259; tuturor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nbeneficiare sau, în cazul unei diviz&#259;ri <span class=SpellE>par&#355;iale</span>\nsau al unei diviz&#259;ri prin separare, tuturor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nbeneficiare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ncare face obiectul diviz&#259;rii, <span class=SpellE>propor&#355;ional</span>\ncu cota din activul net repartizat&#259; fiec&#259;reia potrivit proiectului de\ndivizare transfrontalier&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_192817258\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1188\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_192817258\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)<span class=SpellE>Ac&#355;iunile</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ile</span> sociale sau alte titluri de valoare\nreprezentând capitalul social la una dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nbeneficiare nu pot fi schimbate cu <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span> sociale sau alte titluri de valoare\nreprezentând capitalul social la societatea care face obiectul diviz&#259;rii,\natunci când <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ile</span>\nsociale sau alte titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social sunt <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;inute</span> fie de c&#259;tre societatea <span\nclass=SpellE>îns&#259;&#351;i</span>, fie prin intermediul unei persoane <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionând</span> în nume propriu, dar în contul <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>"}